pullrequest.title: Do not export urdf symbols in sdformat 1.4 (-> sdf_1.4)

content.raw:
Now I just see this:
~~~
$ objdump -T libsdformat.so | grep urdf | c++filt
0000000000077a90  w   DF .text	00000000000000a5  Base        boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Collision>* std::__copy_move_backward<false, false, std::random_access_iterator_tag>::__copy_move_b<boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Collision>*, boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Collision>*>(boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Collision>*, boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Collision>*, boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Collision>*)
0000000000076640  w   DF .text	0000000000000049  Base        void std::_Destroy_aux<false>::__destroy<boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Collision>*>(boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Collision>*, boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Collision>*)
0000000000077de0  w   DF .text	00000000000000a5  Base        boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Visual>* std::__copy_move_backward<false, false, std::random_access_iterator_tag>::__copy_move_b<boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Visual>*, boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Visual>*>(boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Visual>*, boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Visual>*, boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Visual>*)
0000000000074a60  w   DF .text	00000000000000a7  Base        sdf::Console::ConsoleStream& sdf::Console::ConsoleStream::operator<< <urdf::Joint::{unnamed type#1}>(urdf::Joint::{unnamed type#1} const&)
00000000000747a0  w   DF .text	00000000000000a7  Base        sdf::Console::ConsoleStream& sdf::Console::ConsoleStream::operator<< <urdf::Geometry::{unnamed type#1}>(urdf::Geometry::{unnamed type#1} const&)
0000000000076a40  w   DF .text	0000000000000049  Base        void std::_Destroy_aux<false>::__destroy<boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Visual>*>(boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Visual>*, boost::shared_ptr<urdf::Visual>*)
~~~
Not sure if these are a problem.

EDIT: maybe the ConsoleStream ones are from [parser_urdf.cc:1731](#!/osrf/sdformat/src/6a3e4fb70f367d43efd83910417bd00819133120/src/parser_urdf.cc?at=default#cl-1731) and [parser_urdf.cc:2413](#!/osrf/sdformat/src/6a3e4fb70f367d43efd83910417bd00819133120/src/parser_urdf.cc?at=default#cl-2413)
